'''麥克·柏比葛利亞'''（Mike Birbiglia；{{bd|1978年|6月20日}}）是美國的一位喜劇演員、作家、演員和導演。他是一位義大利後裔<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.stltoday.com/entertainment/movies/reviews/comedian-birbiglia-invites-us-to-sleepwalk/article_8ccc2dd8-fc7f-11e1-8e1c-0019bb30f31a.html|title=Comedian Birbiglia invites us to sleepwalk|author=Lee Enterprises|work=stltoday.com|accessdate=2016-03-09|archive-date=2012-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120915012640/http://www.stltoday.com/entertainment/movies/reviews/comedian-birbiglia-invites-us-to-sleepwalk/article_8ccc2dd8-fc7f-11e1-8e1c-0019bb30f31a.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是家中四個孩子中最年幼的一個<ref>{{cite web|url=http://familytreemaker.genealogy.com/users/p/a/t/Edward-J-Patton-NY/WEBSITE-0001/UHP-0733.html|title=Edward-J-Patton-NY - User Trees - Genealogy.com|publisher=|accessdate=2016-03-09|archive-date=2014-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140821161421/http://familytreemaker.genealogy.com/users/p/a/t/Edward-J-Patton-NY/WEBSITE-0001/UHP-0733.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，就讀於[[喬治城大學|喬治城大學]]
